About this property

Spacious Accommodations: Amber Echoland MrT in Hakuba offers a spacious chalet with four bedrooms and five bathrooms. The living room features a sofa and dining area, ensuring comfort for all guests. Modern Amenities: Guests enjoy free WiFi, air-conditioning, and a fully equipped kitchenette. Additional facilities include a hot tub, 24-hour front desk, concierge service, and free on-site private parking. Convenient Location: Located 41 mi from Matsumoto Airport, the chalet is an 18-minute walk from Happo-One Ski Resort and 0.9 mi from Hakuba Happo Bus Terminal. Nearby attractions include Tsugaike Kogen Ski Area (5.6 mi) and Hakuba Cortina Ski Area (9.9 mi).

Company info

Jade Group is a premier hospitality provider in Hakuba, offering a diverse range of accommodations tailored to every traveler. Each of our properties has its own unique charm and character, all united by our dedication to exceptional service, comfort, and an unforgettable guest experience.

Property info

Raise the blinds in your upstairs living room and take in the stunning panoramic views—lush forests at the back and breathtaking ski slopes in the front. Located in the Misorano area of Echoland, this chalet is designed for ultimate relaxation, featuring two cozy sofas, a 65-inch 4K TV equipped with Netflix, YouTube, Video, and Karaoke, and in-floor heating that extends throughout the chalet, ensuring warmth and comfort. Adjacent to the living area, the dining space is thoughtfully designed for both convenience and style. It boasts a stocked mini wine cellar, a fully equipped kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances, a coffee maker, and a beautiful dining table with ample seating—perfect for shared meals and memorable gatherings. All of this is set beneath an impressive 5-meter-high ceiling, creating a sense of openness and warmth that will make you feel right at home when you're not out exploring Hakuba’s endless adventures.

Neighborhood info

The property is located in the vibrant Echoland area, known for its abundance of restaurants, cafés, and bars. Its prime location offers both convenience and efficiency for guests, whether you're heading out for dinner, exploring the town, or catching a shuttle to the ski slopes, everything is easily accessible. Despite being in a lively neighborhood, Member Echoland is tucked away in a quieter section of the Amber Echoland complex, allowing you to enjoy both the energy of the area and the serenity of a peaceful retreat. While not directly connected to the slopes, Jade Group guests can take advantage of our complimentary shuttle service for effortless access to Hakuba’s ski resorts.
